stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending
    pending --> running: atomic claim + lease
    running --> completed: stage committed
    running --> retry: retryable error
    retry --> running: available_at reached
    running --> dead: fatal error or attempts exhausted
    running --> pending: lease expired
    pending --> cancelled: safe admin cancellation
    retry --> cancelled: safe admin cancellation
    completed --> [*]
    dead --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]

    note right of running
      heavy semaphore = 1
      light semaphore = 2
      inference outside DB transaction
    end note

